  • Classes in taxi.model used by taxi.model 
    Class and Description
    Customer
    The Customer class implements all customers using the taxi service.
    Evaluation
    The Evaluation class implements all evaluations made by customers, for a pair of Request-Route.
    Request
    The Request class implements all requests made from a customer to a taxi.
    Route
    The Route class implements all routes requested by customers, and connected with their requests.

    The Taxi class implements all taxis using the taxi service.
